like a cradle ♪

43:48.499 --> 43:53.532
♪ Climb to the treetops, child
if you're able ♪

43:55.365 --> 44:00.999
♪ Let your hands tie a knot
across the table ♪

44:02.732 --> 44:05.165
♪ Come and touch ♪

44:05.232 --> 44:08.332
♪ The things you cannot feel ♪

44:09.399 --> 44:13.365
♪ And close your fingertips ♪

44:13.432 --> 44:17.932
♪ And fly where
I can't hold you ♪

44:17.999 --> 44:20.399
♪ Let the sun rain fall ♪

44:20.465 --> 44:25.032
♪ And let the dewy clouds
enfold you ♪

44:25.099 --> 44:32.765
♪ And maybe you can sing to me
the words I just told you ♪

44:32.832 --> 44:37.865
♪ If all the things you feel
ain't what they seem ♪

44:37.932 --> 44:41.999
♪ Then don't mind me ♪

44:42.065 --> 44:48.599
♪ 'Cause I ain't nothin'
but a dream ♪

44:48.665 --> 44:56.365
♪ And you can follow
And you can follow ♪

44:56.432 --> 45:00.199
♪ And you can follow ♪

